data.description:
This gorgeous two-story house awaits you. Enter into the spacious family room with tall ceilings and abundant natural light. The kitchen offers open floor plan that is adjacent to the well appointed living room ideal for catching up on Netflix or family game night!

This home features double en suites. The primary bedroom is a highly functional on suite with walk-in closet. The second private en suite is located upstairs.  In addition to the double en suites, this home also features a dedicated guest bathroom downstairs. 

The ficus lined backyard posts and adorable patio perfect for entertaining and grilling steaks for the game on Sunday. 

This unique Stone Ridge home is one that you will not want to miss! This two level two bed three bath home feature some of the best amenities Arizona has to offer. Whether golfing at the championship golf course, dining, or just enjoying the live music at the clubhouse with a drink, you will find yourself endlessly entertained by the abundance of activities and the charming natural beauty that surrounds this wonderful home. Located within walking distance to the community center (see amenities) clubhouse, and a beautiful lush green park, ideal for evening stroll or sunrise walks with the dogs. The homes in this area are in high demand so don't wait come see it today and one visit we have you convinced!
